{{韩国料理}}
'''包饭酱'''（{{lang|ko|쌈장}}）是[[韩国料理|韩国料理]]中的一种糊状辣味[[酱料|酱料]]，通常用作[[菜包肉|菜包肉]]的蘸酱。包饭酱主要由[[大酱|大酱]]、[[苦椒酱|苦椒酱]]、[[麻油|麻油]]、[[洋葱|洋葱]]、[[蒜|蒜]]、[[青葱|青葱]]、[[红糖|红糖]]等制成。.<ref>{{ko}} [http://krdic.naver.com/detail.nhn?docid=24295600&re=y Ssamjang] {{Wayback|url=http://krdic.naver.com/detail.nhn?docid=24295600&re=y |date=20161020112440 }} at [[Doosan_Encyclopedia|Doosan Encyclopedia]]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hannaone.com/Recipe/Ssamjang.html |title=Ssamjang recipe |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2019-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507071119/https://hannaone.com/Recipe/Ssamjang.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chow.com/recipes/13682 |title=Ssamjang recipe |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2010-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100309043538/http://www.chow.com/recipes/13682 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.trifood.com/ssamjang.html |title=Ssamjang recipe |access-date=2016-10-19 |archive-date=2010-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101129003621/http://trifood.com/ssamjang.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

除了标准的包饭酱外，有时还会加上其他原料以制成各种类的包饭酱，包括坚果包饭酱（{{lang|ko|견과류 쌈장}}）、章鱼包饭酱（{{lang|ko|쭈꾸미 쌈장}}）、豆腐包饭酱（{{lang|ko|두부 쌈장}}）、飞鱼籽包饭酱（{{lang|ko|날치알 쌈장}}）、拌菜包饭酱（{{lang|ko|나물 쌈장}}）等。<ref>{{ko}} [http://www.segye.com/Articles/NEWS/CULTURE/Article.asp?aid=20100415003413&subctg1=&subctg2= Mom's ssamjang] {{Wayback|url=http://www.segye.com/Articles/NEWS/CULTURE/Article.asp?aid=20100415003413&subctg1=&subctg2= |date=20120304212819 }}, Segye Ilbo, 2010-04-15.Retrieved 2010-06-25.</ref>

